      "releaseNotes": "Choose your Start on page — open directly to Homepage, a model, Local Vehicles, Alerts, or Acceleration Boost\nNew option to Place Viewed Vehicles at the Bottom of the filter to keep fresh listings at the top\nCopy VIN from vehicle details with a tap\nAlert finds now show miles away from your home zip\nOne-time notices for build sheet images and seller verification on vehicle details\nImproved notification handling and various bug fixes",
