      "currency": "USD",
      "description": "This application lists Tesla vehicles with the Full Self Driving Capability - Included Package, Enhanced Autopilot (EAP) or Acceleration boost available for sale in the U.S.A. and Canada. FSD,EAP or Acceleration Boost cars should bring a premium to the used car.  With FSD Hunter, we do the hard part of looking for the 1-2% of cars that are listed with these packages, scan for software screen or find based on vehicle build sheet, and display them in our app.  Saving you hours of time and thousands of cars that you do not have to look through yourself.   When you find a vehicle you like, simply tap the heart icon to add to your favorites. \n\nNow including Canadian vehicles with limited results. (less than 20 FSD, less than 12 EAP, less than 20 Acceleration Boost)\n*HI, AK - Cars are found but on a limited basis as there are fewer vehicles to search.",
